org.forgerock.openidm.smartevent.core

Class DisruptorReferringPublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.smartevent.core.DisruptorReferringPublisher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PluggablePublisher

    public class DisruptorReferringPublisher
extends Object
implements PluggablePublisher
    Publisher that uses the disruptor pattern and RingBuffer to process events in a highly concurrent manner. Start event issues EventEntry without limitation on the outstanding start/end events, making it suitable for long(er) time span events/measurements
